				<p>The BBC charged us at Aardman with making a couple of prototype interactive videos to user test how people engaged with different types of e-learning content. This was mine; layers of 2D Flash animation layered up in After Effects in a 3D space, with a layer of parallaxing animation over the top (created in Flash and exported with CreateJS), and then a layer of HTML over the top for accessible learning content. Layers! Can't link here, but <a href="mailto:georgehenryrowe@gmail.com">email me</a> if you want to play with it.</p>

